Package me.gamercoder215.socketmc.spigot

Class SocketPlugin

java.lang.Object
me.gamercoder215.socketmc.spigot.SocketPlugin
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class SocketPlugin extends Object implements Serializable
Wrapper class around a Plugin object to be serialized and sent to the mod. Used for logging, settings, and other information purposes. In the eventuality that a Plugin object is not available, use UNKNOWN.
